oh and .. i went to the tae kwon do tournment and iw on second place out of the womens divison ..i fought nicole my homie but won =] then a 35-40 yr old woment ( not sure of age ) she was a 4th degree blackbelt and i beat her two i gave her a bloody nose ..whoop whoop then this really ghetto dominican chick i knocked her outta the rign like 6 times but i made her nose bleed and she cried so she got pity points..but idk all the masters sed i won and like the people were all like cheering me on and stuff .. it was so cool.. omg i punched er square in the face..and she was hysterical to stop the fight..in the beginning she got me with a really hard kick to the head and i just took it yay.. anyways i also judeged sparring and patterns for various fights.. i actually had fun and like it was cool having nicole and everone cheer me on ..and this is my first time winning .. and like idk im not an angry persona nd i neer look for a fight but i improved so much i rele did sum serious ass kicking lmao...okay anyways umm all in all it was a good day and i had so much fun i love tae kwon do and i mite test 4 second degree =]..okay enuf of that iluu all <3 skye

okay so ..wow this year was so amazing..no wonder it was sold out!..which i cant believe but it really was.!?!? so by a miracle of my dad ..and jill<3 i got tickets for it the day before =] i went with tekla and zain.. my dad drove us =] i got there at around 1 so i missed the starting line .. but its okay =\.. then the minute i got there i saw DEV and ADRI<33333333 which was totally awsome we bought some water got the time list..and walked around .. then we so avenged sevenfold..and then we went on to see ..senses fail..Atreyu..then bumped into abed grace dina sammy gabby and sam<3 in my chemical romance.. we got close to the front.. and then thats when things got amazingly fun =]...tekla crowd surfed!?!?!?! and then i did..and i saw abed crowd curfing too lmao that was so awsome everyone had such an awsome time =]...then we went to the offspring and that was effin awsomee..grace abed zain and me saw some guy with his ankle turned like 90 degrees to the left which was pretty gross ..i saw some girl like run outta the crowd and violently puke and i was squashed btwn a bunch of dirty sweaty people.. but thats warped tour a lot of dirt great music and friends =].. i think tekla and zain and i can all agree the most fun was FALL OUT BOY aside from me knowing all the words to every song they played =D.. i got to go soo closeeee...i even got to save like 3 girls and a guy who almost fell but i caught them =].. and i saved zain's hat twice yay lol.. omg the feeling of pure happiness of just being in the crowd screaming and singling along with everywun was just amazing..and the whole day was just crazy and full of fun.. when i first arrived at warped tour i saw all these extremly dirty people..and its funny because i left dirtier than most ..we all did.. but it was awsome.. when i got home after dropping tekla and zain off .. i took the onli shower..and took two asprin cuz i had a horrible headache and went to sleep.. it was definitly one of the best days ever and i cant wait till warped tour next year!?!?!?!? dedicated to everyone who i got to chill w at warped tour =] yayaya
okay are you ready? I CAN GO TO WARPED TOUR WHOOOO!!!! i got tickets yeayay!!!!! ahh im so happi =] this makes my summer <33

"..Turning to you is lke falling in love when your down.."-DC heres some lyrics on how i feel.. dont you see that the charade is OVER and all the best deceptions and the clever cover story awards go to you so kiss me hard cuz this will be the last time that i let you you will be back someday and this akward kiss that screams of other peoples lips will be of service to keeping you away i heard about your regrets i heard that you were feeling sorry guess i should have heard of that from you id rather say nothing i rather you never heard my voice you do not warrent long gbyes your calling to late..

alright so i just typed this big-huge-emotional entry and now i just highlighted the whole thing and deleted it..no use in complaining i doubt it will make anything better.. alright so basically heres a more low-key less dramatic email..last nite..i hung out with micha and tekla and i was allowed to stay out until 10 which it pretty late for me..cuz lockdown..but like no-one was out but i still hadd fun..=] opening the bottles was ghetto-crazy..lolol...on the way to the bleachers on shore we saw fire works from coney island..they were so pretty..micha tekla and i ..just stood there watchin them..it was so romantic<33 lol jk jk..tekla started singing a spanish love song and we just were hysterical laughin...then i got kinda sick bcuz before that i had a huge ice-cream sunday..but all in all it was an okay nite..then this morning i woke up with monster cramps and like..my dad wanted me to go running and i refused so now im not allowed out until..i run 3 miles =\...whatever..then after i woke up ..my brother had to be taken to the hospital, and my mom was hysterical crying..all he has is a sinus infection and so his eye is like really swollen but hell b fine he just has to get checked and like cleaned out or w.e..but my mom is a drama queen and shes like not talkin to me ..so i left and came downstairs to my gmas house =] she always makes me feel better about EVERYTHING..anyway..i was watching my other little brother tommy hes 5.. we were watching the berenstein bears show on pbs kids ( oh man i used to love those books<33)...anyway at the end of the episode there was a line where they said.. " the difference btwn having a horrible time and a great time..is just how you look at it.." and i guess with a lot of things thats truu....idk w my mom freaking out and my parents being anal..i wish i could call this one person and talk to them ..they always make me feel better..ugh this sucks so bad..i dont really want to get into it in this entry but like i just miss so much our friendship and stuff..that whole " tell you everything" type of thing and talking until 5am and all that stuff.. idk... but ya kno whatever i dont need a guy to make me happi? right? lol i think ill be okay =]..alright well im guna go love you all<3 thanks for listening .if u rd this ..COMMENT<33 .. later<3Skye "..I think you lost what you loved in that mess of details. They seemed so important at the time but now you can't even recall any of the names, faces, or lines. It is more the feeling of it all.." -idk where this is from but i like it "But there was once you...You said you hated my suffering.. and You understood.. and you take care of me...Said you would always be there... Well where are you now??.." -bright eyes "..our ways will never change Hate me now so I can move on Make it easier to see that you're gone All the things they're gone too Turn and changed into memories I'm coming over but it never was enough I thought it through and my worst brings out the best in you Because im waiting for something that you'll never give me.."

To reach you upstairs. I thought I heard you call out for more. I know that's crazy. I'm pretty sure that I'm lost again. It won't get through to you. I won't get through. I think I won't get through... "..your owening up to nothing and i wish that i was gone...its clouded and so is my head the hint of these new tears shine..and i try to choke them bak but im useless im useless against them on the way home this story is my confession and i think ill take the long way"
